The paper introduces a new model for sublinear algorithms and studies a fundamental graph optimization problem of computing a maximum matching. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational geometry (cs.CG), information theory (cs.IT), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
